{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-detail-js","path":"/en/software-development-bait/","result":{"data":{"prismicProject":{"id":"822cb6c0-4d58-5dae-b0c5-4a3a6e43e339","lang":"en","data":{"featured_image":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5009380863039399,"src":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=400&h=300","srcSet":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=100&h=67 100w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=200&h=133 200w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=400&h=267 400w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=600&h=400 600w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/0aacb798-27d2-4374-98d4-f37f60a66faa_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=800&h=533 800w","sizes":""}},"call_to_action":[{"cta_button_text":{"text":"GET IN TOUCH"},"cta_description":{"raw":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"You too can benefit from our wide range of services across software development, UX/UI design and marketing support. Just get in touch to discuss your next project!","spans":[]}]},"cta_link":{"url":"https://www.labzone.tech/contact"}}],"project_summary":{"text":"Accelerating the client's web footprint while implementing UX/UI principles is at the heart of what we do. Read how we strengthened BAIT's technology proposition to a media audience. ","html":"<p>Accelerating the client&#39;s web footprint while implementing UX/UI principles is at the heart of what we do. Read how we strengthened BAIT&#39;s technology proposition to a media audience. </p>"},"project_title":{"text":"Accelerating BAIT's technology proposition to a media audience "},"result":{"html":"<h3>UX/UI focused business website that supports BAIT&#39;s value proposition and provision of expert development services</h3><p>One of the projects we delivered for BAIT was the <a  href=\"https://bait.sk/\">bait.sk</a> website development. Detail-oriented UX/UI journey design presented the key element in structuring the information and navigating through a complex topic for the end-user. As the visual designs were provided by the client, our responsibility was to qualify the UX/UI approach and code the website per requirements. </p><p>The whole project was delivered in an extremely speedy turnaround of x weeks, with client satisfaction resulting in the venture of using our other services.</p><h3>Utilising/leveraging our development capabilities</h3><p>As the trust and the relationship soared over 3 years, BAIT was looking for an agile development team that had powerful front and back-end capabilities. Our independent global team ticked all the boxes and therefore was selected to collaborate on several unique projects over the years. </p><p>BAIT had a particular interest in the usage of our front-end developers and their in-depth knowledge of Vue.js  and CSS (SASS) technologies. </p><p>Key projects delivered:</p><ul><li>Creation of a new front-end layer for <a  href=\"https://funradio.sk\">https://funradio.sk</a> and its strategy using a modern stack language. The main challenge faced was the requirement of bending the new front-end around proprietary BAIT CMS. Due to the performance reasons such as specific caching, we weren&#39;t allowed to build a website as a Single Page Application. Our solution was a semi-SPA/hybrid architecture that satisfied back-end platform requirements and followed the proposed UX. This was of the utmost importance when building a completely <a  href=\"https://www.funradio.sk/player/?stream=live\">new online radio player</a>.</li><li>Development of 2019 IIHF World Championship tracking/score-guessing micro application  - main challenge was the code translation of hockey rules, Championship rules and scoring system implementing UI logic. The fact that end-users were working the scoring app to predict unplayed matches made the entire project even more complex as it had to time-lock certain branches of the app once the initial groups have played.</li><li>Development of the largest Slovak advertising portal - <a  href=\"https://avizo.sk/\">Avizo</a>. Currently completed first release aimed at the general public. Our team delivered static UI patterns, several JavaScript modules and consulting on overall front-end architecture and code seed (foundational code base and scaffolding setup).</li></ul><p>These complex projects require quick thinking outside of the box while delivering innovative and functional solutions. As a team, we love to be challenged and our partner BAIT never disappoints.</p><p>We&#39;re delighted to work with BAIT while keeping the finger on the pulse on the technology and entertainment industry. </p>"},"assignment":{"html":"<h3>Digitally present a complex IT and CMS technology brand to a targeted audience and providing front-end development outsourcing</h3><p>BAIT is a specialised IT and CMS platform based company, founded back in 2005 by a group of IT and media enthusiasts. Headquartered in Ivanka pri Dunaji, Slovakia with an international branch in Czechia, BAIT&#39;s main focus is offering niche-targeted development services such as the creation of their own CMS systems for the media industry, game development services and enterprise integration solutions. One of their most prominent clients is <strong>FUN MEDIA GROUP</strong> which covers Fun radio (leading Slovak radio station with 30% market share for age group 14-54), spravy.sk and few other portals.</p><p>The client is a leading technology and CMS expert, with only a handful of competitors in its field. Due to the nature of its business, the need for a strong UX driven digital identity only appeared in the last year.</p>"},"technologies":{"text":"vue, react, sass, bootstrap"},"team":{"html":"<ul><li>3x Frontend Developer</li></ul>"},"testimonials":[{"blockquote":{"text":"Working with LabZone is always great. They're very professional, yet friendly and the remote communication is always at high level. The front-ends provided by them are the best I've worked with and they always show patience and goodwill when integrating to our back-end systems."},"footer":{"text":"Matej Žilák, CTO"},"testimonial_image":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=400&h=300","srcSet":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=100&h=100 100w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=200&h=200 200w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=400&h=400 400w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=600&h=600 600w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/4311a765-7c72-4836-a74d-0a6b59da2276_matej-zilak-bait.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=800&h=800 800w","sizes":""}}}],"body":[{"__typename":"PrismicProjectBodyImageGallery","id":"4af483b6-e340-559e-ac24-3e458f162c8f","items":[{"caption":{"text":"Bait hero carousel"},"alt_text":{"text":"Bait hero carousel"},"image":{"thumb":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.6528925619834711,"src":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/04316a75-34e7-4ed0-8129-28de07aa2d1a_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=270&h=270","srcSet":"https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/04316a75-34e7-4ed0-8129-28de07aa2d1a_bait-main.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&w=68&h=41 68w, https://images.prismic.io/labzonetech/04316a75-34e7-4ed0-8129-28de07aa2